{"tid":276161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【淘寶慎中伏】500噸韓舊衫走私入內地 「產自」殮房洗淨轉售","createTime":"2017-06-08T15:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T16:40:23.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0cb4befa496bedf6da77b1a5de9705ee677d1b","tid":276161,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"【淘寶慎中伏】500噸韓舊衫走私入內地 「產自」殮房洗淨轉售<br />\n<br />\n（新增：影片）<br />\n<br />\n淘寶買產自南韓的時裝，小心買到死者衫！福建廈門海關近日查獲一宗海上偷運走私「洋垃圾」案件，查獲來自南韓3,596包舊衣服、共計500噸。這些衣服帶有明顯污漬，部分內衣上甚至還有疑似血漬。當局指，這些舊衣來自國外二手市場，甚至殮房，更可能有菌。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月中旬，廈門海關緝私局接獲線報指，有走私分子從境外偷運一批舊服裝到內地，再轉運往其他地區清洗銷售。海關緝私隊隨即加強巡查，上月26日晚10時終在廈門附近海域發現，一艘名為「億發」號的貨輪故意關閉了AIS（船舶自動識別系統），形跡極為可疑。海關人員登船後，查獲該批舊衣服。<br />\n<br />\n在清點過程中，廈門海關發現了大量舊童裝。「這些舊服裝大都來自國外二手市場、太平間等，未經任何殺菌消毒程序，往往攜帶大量的傳染病菌，屬於國家禁止進口的『洋垃圾』。」據廈門海關隸屬漳州海關緝私分局情報科副科長章睿郁表示，這些衣服經過簡單分揀、漂洗後，將流入夜市、地攤、網店等渠道銷售，嚴重影響公眾健康。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170608/56799565\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170608%2F56799565&h=4a694a3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3eebec3ff90529e7faa2f7ef94795d1fb37fcbf","tid":276161,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170608/56799565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170608%2F56799565&d=iOPvj4WU1MgCj6%2FE9Hyrgb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1dc5c106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170608%2F56799565&h=b22a9462\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170608/56799565</a>"},{"pid":"1b7f0decb48729bd6819107e417e17c91152ab75","tid":276161,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"港女著死人衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731d62305fa6e01a455dcbed8d64751899d9b5bd","tid":276161,"uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"Oppa著過既衫，我想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331c3cd4934a19acf6d3a5a1b927a867cfd1bb25","tid":276161,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fff20852795dcbfcd5fcd8b21baeb8ca9b89270b","tid":276161,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"親~"},{"pid":"2ee1b4c613d7b774ea5723aebb8fc44244467c42","tid":276161,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"邊會係殯儀館呀<br />\n<br />\n幫死人著幾十件衫咩"},{"pid":"2ec51f75436544e0dea77504071ce224d5d3900f","tid":276161,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真我想知佢哋點賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話d衫係古著<br />\n大把人爭住買"},{"pid":"2b8a458fd5a361823d22f6cd3d73494a977483f5","tid":276161,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"好環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c1c0d58e0ae0207239a390f864645622417fd7","tid":276161,"uid":104941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真我想知佢哋點賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話d衫係古著<br />\n大把人爭住買</blockquote><br />\n香討班ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}